text: George Raymond Kinley (June 4, 1937 â€“ February 23, 2022) was an American politician and businessman. He was born in Akron, Ohio. He was in the Iowa Senate from 1973 to 1992, and in the Iowa House of Representatives from 1971 to 1973. Kinley was a member of the Democratic Party. Kinley died on February 23, 2022 in Des Moines, Iowa at the age of 84.George R.
